text: Bikbau () is a rural locality (a selo) in Bikbausky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 199 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 17 km from Isyangulovo, 4 km from Trushino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Bikbau
